Title: audit_log: retrieve and clear the audit log
Class: feature
Compatible: compat
Component: rest-api
Date: 1692353538
Edition: cre
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 1
Version: 2.3.0b1


This werk introduces a new set of endpoints to the REST API to operate the audit log. Users can now perform the following actions via the REST API:

* Get audit logs per day
* Clear the audit log
